data.message: Question for Amy: Will there be synergy, or just friendship at the event?

message:
Words of the wise Amy Underwood:

Just a couple days until the women's lock-in which also means there's only a couple more day of class!!!! WOOHOO!! Are you thinking, "Gee, I'm going to have so much studying to do, I don't think I can go"? Well, let me just remind you that Thursday is study day and you deserve a night of fun to celebrate the end of classes. Still not convinced? Here's a list of the awesome things that await you at the lock-in:
-Snacks 
-Competition
-Friendship
-Destressing
-Movies
-Holiday Spirit
-Mug & Muffin
-LOTS OF LOVE AND FUN
So, go ahead and RSVP to the event and put it on the G-cal!!! SEE YOU THERE!!! (If you can only come for part of it, still come!)
